We decided to hold Positive Image at its launch price until v1.1 was
released. As this has now happened, we  reserve the right to revert to
full RRP of 79 pounds at any time. Having said that, the current price
remains at 65 pounds + P&P  (2  pounds  UK, 5 pounds Europe, 10 pounds
rest of world). UK customers can pay by cheque, Postal Order or Credit
Card  (except  Switch).  Overseas  customers  should  order  from  our
distributor in their country (  list  follows).  If  we  do not have a
distributor they can of  course  order  direct from Floppyshop. Please
note that when ordering from  Floppyshop,  payment  must be made in UK
pounds sterling. The easiest way is to pay by credit card, but we also
accept Eurocheques, International Money Orders  and Post Giros (in all
cases they must be made out  in  UK  pounds  sterling)  or by way of a
cheque drawn on a UK bank.

